{
  "id": "adv_event_2508_01_02",
  "title": "忘れない\nために",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "さて。あいつら説得して、解散撤回させないと\nkanaはどこほっつき歩いてるか分かりませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さて。あいつら説得して、解散撤回させないと\nkanaはどこほっつき歩いてるか分かりませんけど",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.7916327477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "mihoはとりあえずアパートにはいるでしょうし\nまずは、そっちから行ってみますかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "mihoはとりあえずアパートにはいるでしょうし\nまずは、そっちから行ってみますかね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9,
      "endTime": 14.322403717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺も同席しましょうか？　二人だけじゃ不安……\nいえ、万が一の時の仲裁役ってことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "俺も同席しましょうか？　二人だけじゃ不安……\nいえ、万が一の時の仲裁役ってことで",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "endTime": 21.613333543099998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、別にいいです。って言うか、むしろ邪魔です\n{user}さんってmihoの地雷ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "いや、別にいいです。って言うか、むしろ邪魔です\n{user}さんってmihoの地雷ですし",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8217007954,
      "endTime": 29.6095238049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.8217007954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺が地雷ってことは、もしかして\nmihoさんが辞めたがる理由は葉さん絡み……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "俺が地雷ってことは、もしかして\nmihoさんが辞めたがる理由は葉さん絡み……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8217007954,
      "endTime": 37.1186170894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "さあ。それは本人に聞いて下さい\nま、今は来てもmihoが意固地になるだけですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さあ。それは本人に聞いて下さい\nま、今は来てもmihoが意固地になるだけですよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3269843418,
      "endTime": 44.719024880599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.9269838332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは私がやるので、{user}さんは\n頼んだ『あれ』の方を、ちゃんとお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こっちは私がやるので、{user}さんは\n頼んだ『あれ』の方を、ちゃんとお願いしますね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9269838332,
      "endTime": 51.994489479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.2436504999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人は、また帰宅時間の連絡もなしに……\n人に夕飯作らせるだけ作らせておいて、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あの二人は、また帰宅時間の連絡もなしに……\n人に夕飯作らせるだけ作らせておいて、まったく",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2936504999,
      "endTime": 63.1016775767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.2936504999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、家が静かなのは結構なことね\nそれに、あの二人との付き合いも、もうすぐ終わるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……まぁ、家が静かなのは結構なことね\nそれに、あの二人との付き合いも、もうすぐ終わるし",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2936504999,
      "endTime": 71.8248068491,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
