        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8706.348991500008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.9999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまー。まだ夕飯食べてないんだけど、何かある？\nあ、白いご飯と味噌汁！　久しぶりの日本の味！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ただいまー。まだ夕飯食べてないんだけど、何かある？\nあ、白いご飯と味噌汁！　久しぶりの日本の味！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5936494826,
      "endTime": 83.8519939421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.3269828159
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.0603161493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、食べていいとは誰も言ってないわよ\n日本から持って来るの大変だったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ちょっと、食べていいとは誰も言ってないわよ\n日本から持って来るの大変だったんだから",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0603161493,
      "endTime": 90.2819942156,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6773.017184000011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.4936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "はいこれ、kanaが飲んじゃったかわりのワイン\n味噌汁の分くらいは、先に飲んでいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はいこれ、kanaが飲んじゃったかわりのワイン\n味噌汁の分くらいは、先に飲んでいいわよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4936494826,
      "endTime": 96.7667787551,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10877.204319599998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.9603161493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、貴方に酒を奢られる日がくるなんて\nふぅん……貴方のチョイスにしては、味はまあまあね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "まさか、貴方に酒を奢られる日がくるなんて\nふぅん……貴方のチョイスにしては、味はまあまあね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9603161493,
      "endTime": 107.6087286631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.3708538022
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.7936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "うわ、一瞬でボトルの半分まで減った\n説得のお供に買ってきたけど、終わるまでもつかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うわ、一瞬でボトルの半分まで減った\n説得のお供に買ってきたけど、終わるまでもつかしら",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7936494826,
      "endTime": 117.0344205855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.2269828159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "で、さあ。あんたがスリクスを解散したいのは\nうちじゃ、昔の相棒の宣伝を出来ないからってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "で、さあ。あんたがスリクスを解散したいのは\nうちじゃ、昔の相棒の宣伝を出来ないからってこと？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2269828159,
      "endTime": 127.2894320804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.4936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ乱暴にまとめてくれたわね……でも、そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だいぶ乱暴にまとめてくれたわね……でも、そうね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.4936494826,
      "endTime": 132.93335466370002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "葉ちゃんを忘れてほしくないのに、スリクスにいても\n彼女のことは思い出してももらえない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "葉ちゃんを忘れてほしくないのに、スリクスにいても\n彼女のことは思い出してももらえない",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1269828159,
      "endTime": 139.40920489619998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.5936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "なら、私達で昔の曲をカバーとかすれば良くない？\n別に、そのくらいだったら付き合ってもいいわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "なら、私達で昔の曲をカバーとかすれば良くない？\n別に、そのくらいだったら付き合ってもいいわよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.5936494826,
      "endTime": 148.31031646710002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.5269828159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "だからさ、そのー、解散ちょっと考え直して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だからさ、そのー、解散ちょっと考え直して……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5269828159,
      "endTime": 153.9960077602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
